{"article_id":"OJCnlq7jWLH0Mp8U","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"\" The 360 \" shows you diverse perspectives on the day ' s top stories and debates .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Supreme Court has narrowly blocked the Trump administration ' s bid","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to end the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"( DACA )","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"program .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The Obama-era policy protects hundreds of thousands of young immigrants","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"who were brought to the U.S. as children from deportation","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and allows them to work legally .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"While the Trump administration is undisputedly authorized to rescind the DACA program ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"the justices ruled 5-4","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that the administration had failed to follow proper procedure","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"and violated the Administrative Procedure Act in its attempt","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"to end the program .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"who broke with his conservative colleagues ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"wrote in the majority opinion","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that the administration did not provide an adequate explanation","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"for ending the program .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"In the court ' s main dissent , Justice Clarence Thomas wrote","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that the DACA program is unlawful .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Only Justice Sonia Sotomayor concluded","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that the administration was motivated by race in its attempt","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to rescind the program .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"There ' s widespread bipartisan support for DACA recipients ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"known as \" Dreamers. \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The court ' s decision has been especially celebrated by Dreamers and immigration advocates .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"However , the ruling does not enshrine the DACA program in law","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and leaves the door open for the Trump administration to renew its efforts","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to end it .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"While the decision reduces some uncertainty over the immediate future of Dreamers ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"advocates say","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"that they ' re still vulnerable","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"because the program is not enforced by law .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Congress must pass a law","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"to protect Dreamers ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"they say .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Until Congress creates a solution ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"Dreamers will continue to be used as a political bargaining chip ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"they say .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"But upholding DACA gives Congress little reason","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"to act ,","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"others argue .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"With DACA in place ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"there is no incentive","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"to force lawmakers to the table","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"to create a permanent solution .","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"Politically , it ' s expected that DACA will become a campaign issue .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Many believe","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that the court ' s ruling and the future of the program will be debated on the 2020 trail","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"especially since immigration reform is a signature part of Trump ' s platform .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Most immigration experts say","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"there isn ' t enough time","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"for Trump to rescind DACA before the November election .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Some pundits say","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"it ' s a huge political risk to try to end a program","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"that a majority of Americans want passed into law","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and that Trump should simply let the issue fade away .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Others say","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"the ruling is a danger","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"because it shows","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that Trump didn ' t meet one of his 2016 campaign promises .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"However , a second failure","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"to end the program","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"could reflect poorly on Trump during his reelection campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"some say .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Acting Secretary of Homeland Security Chad Wolf said","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"his department will continue to process renewals for current DACA recipients","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"while the Trump administration considers a new legal strategy","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"for ending the program .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"However , it ' s still unclear whether DHS will start processing new applications .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"If elected ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"presumptive Democratic nominee Joe Biden pledged to reinstate DACA and introduce a bill in Congress","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"to create a pathway to citizenship for Dreamers and other undocumented people .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"There are more legal battles ahead .","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"A pending lawsuit by a group of red states argues","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"former President Barack Obama overstepped his constitutional authority","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"in creating DACA","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and could end the program .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"This is a victory for Dreamers ,","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"but there ' s still a fight ahead","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"\" This is undoubtedly a victory ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and yet we know","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"it ' s not permanent .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"The reality is that Trump and his administration continue to attack immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Today ' s victory must inspire all of us to continue to fight. \"","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"- Greisa Martinez Rosas to HuffPost","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"\" Mr . Trump occasionally expresses sympathy for the dreamers ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"but what matters is not what he says","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"but what he does . ... His administration could quickly issue a new memorandum with more careful reasoning","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that the court would presumably uphold. \"","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"- Editorial board , Washington Post","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Until there ' s a permanent solution ,","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"Dreamers will be used as political pawns","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"\" Until Congress acts ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Dreamers will continue to be used as bargaining chips ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"no matter who occupies the White House. \"","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"- Editorial board , Boston Globe","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":175,"right":193,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":167,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":121,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":121,"left":104,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":101,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaborat